ji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市斤真係得弱智支那人先用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明，鄰國唔係好祟尚公制咩？</blockquote><br />\n中國同香港啲單位叫法唔同<br />\n<br />\n就係崇尚用公制先格硬改市斤做1市斤=0.5千克<br />\n中國：1「市斤」=10両=0.5「千克」<br />\n香港：1「斤」=16両=0.605「公斤」<br />\n<br />\n喺香港，有時會因為強調「斤」係指16両嗰種，係會叫「司馬斤」，唔會叫「司馬斤」做「市斤」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/230116_643b641542e4f5ea5d1386d23cc893f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F230116_643b641542e4f5ea5d1386d23cc893f7.jpg&h=97adbc40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08608919d2ec2a0c44276255446f781e0a2c5e5f","tid":489953,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"司徙奈奈都中3啦，你小三收皮啦"},{"pid":"40b060a29ffb98eb195dd4babb6037e4907e621d","tid":489953,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"求奇啦，斤又好公斤又好，磅又好<br />\n有得食咪算，唔好咁撚煩"},{"pid":"20da6c87ca27b605c6d53cd7c620e37206b7e339","tid":489953,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T18:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>司徙奈奈都中3啦，你小三收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我小三都聰明過佢牙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e8b10abc224ec3e603513522dca6fc516daa7f","tid":489953,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9caad7adbd1a46d3e70c093630b3cd337d4863","tid":489953,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9113970d2c1f2ae059f0f6d8a10fe9b34b70e89","tid":489953,"uid":131884,"like